projects.title: Aeternus Argus
projects.description: VPN traffic classifier with XGBoost achieving 95% accuracy
projects.content:
## Overview
Developed under mentorship of Georgia Tech professor, Aeternus Argus is a machine learning system that classifies VPN traffic with 95% accuracy.

## Technical Implementation
- Built XGBoost classifier for encrypted traffic analysis
- Implemented feature engineering pipeline for network packets
- Created real-time classification system

## Results
- 95% classification accuracy
- Paper submitted to academic conference
- Deployed live demo system
